text: Gif ðu ne cunne understandan on ðis ledene þe her beforan awriten is, þonne loca ðu her hu þu scealt þin gear rihtlice gefadian.
ÆfterXVI kalendas februarii, loca hwar beo raþost tyn nihta eald mona.
Æfter ðan on ða sunnanniht þe ðar raðost kymð ðu scealt belucan alleluia.
Gyf se mona byð on sunnandæg tyn nihta eald, þeh ðu scealt nyman þone æftran sunnandæg.
Æfteroctaua idus februarii, loca hwar beoIInihta eald mona, æfter ðan on ðone sunnandæg byð ealda halga dæg.
Æfterduodecima kalendas aprilis, loca hwær beo feowertyne nihta eald mona, æfter ðan on þonne sunnandæg þe þar nehst cymð byð eastordæg.
Æfteroctaua kalendas Maii, loca hwar beo twentig nihta eald mona, þonne on þone <monandæg> æfter sunnandæge ðe ðar nyhst cymþ byð forma gangdæg.
Æfteroctaua idus Maii, loca hwar beo feower nihta eald mona, þonne on þone sunnandæg þe ðar æfter cymð byð pentecostes mæssedæg.
Þis is eal ful soð, fare bisextus swa he fare.
